_sText:
Use of the M4A1 is reccommended because of its suppressor - which means you will be able to hear the headshot noise when you correctly aim.
The upper section is for practicing your grenade throw accuracy.
The lower section is for practicing your spray control or just for fun.
Buy sections in all 3 areas; type sv_cheats 1 and then impulse 101 in console for max money.
Demo video:
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MOzI660tSQw&feature=feedu
